Table 1. Crystal data and structure refinements of 1

| Empirical formula | C84H89Cu7K2N16O131P4W36 |
|-------------------|------------------------|
| M                 | 10683.78               |
| T (K)             | 293(2)                 |
| Crystal system    | Triclinic              |
| Space group       | P-1                    |
| a (Å)             | 16.812(3)              |
| b (Å)             | 17.650(4)              |
| c (Å)             | 17.666(4)              |
| α (°)             | 115.91(3)              |
| β (°)             | 93.08(3)               |
| γ (°)             | 101.93(3)              |
| V (Å³)            | 4550.9(22)              |
| Z                 | 1                      |
| θ range (°)       | 3.01–26.37             |
| Dc (gcm⁻³)        | 3.898                  |
| Abs coeff (mm⁻¹)  | 23.626                 |
| Total data collected | 39057              |
| Unique data       | 17932                  |
| Rint              | 0.1059                 |
| GOF on F²         | 1.026                  |
| Final R indices [I>2σ(I)]a | R1=0.0694, wR2=0.1415 |
| R indices (all data)b | R1=0.1221, wR2=0.1660 |

a R1 = ∑|Fo|-|Fc|/∑|Fo|;
b wR2 = [∑w(|Fo|²-|Fc|²)/∑w(|Fo|²)]¹/²
